description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Mike Florio about the latest on the Deshaun Watson case. What are the chances he plays this season? Reggie Miller makes his weekly appearance and discusses how his comments on Luka Doncic weight a couple months ago may be a factor in his playoff performance.
